  <td>(~INPUTCHECKBOX|inProd4~) Change Manager</td>
  <td>(~INPUTCHECKBOX|inProd5~) DB Optimizer</td>
</tr>
<tr>
  <td>(~INPUTCHECKBOX|inProd6~) DBArtisan</td>
